### Part 1 to 8 - Request for Proposal - Canadian Firearms Digital Services Solution (CFDSS) Project

**Reference Number:** WS4530821977-Doc4530863177
**Amendment Number:** 4
**Solicitation Number:** WS4530821977
**Publication Date :** April 11, 2024
**Tender Closing Date:** May 30, 2024 at 14:00 PM EDT
**Amendment Date:** May 24, 2024

**Procurement Overview:**

The Royal Canadian Mounted Police (RCMP) is seeking a contractor to deliver a functional system for the Canadian Firearms Digital Services Solution (CFDSS) project. The contractor will be expected to bring expertise and experience in delivering major projects, as well as supporting the development and implementation of digital solutions and technologies related to the digitalization of client-facing services.

**Eligibility:**

Only TBIPS SA Holders holding a TBIPS SA for Tier 2 at the time of bid closing, in all required resource categories in this solicitation in the National Capital Region (NCR) Region under the EN578-170432 series of SAs are eligible to compete.

**Notice Details:**

* **Procurement Category:** SRV
* **Procurement Method:** Competitive - Selective Tendering
* **Selection Criteria:** Highest Combined Rating of Technical Merit and Price
* **Trade Agreements:** Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA), Canada-Colombia Free Trade Agreement, Comprehensive and Progressive Agreement for Trans-Pacific Partnership (CPTPP), Canada-Korea Free Trade Agreement (CKFTA), Canada-Chile Free Trade Agreement (CCFTA), and others.
* **Regions of Delivery:** National Capital Region (NCR)
* **Contract Entity:** Department of Public Works and Government Services (PSPC)
* **Contact Information:**
	+ Kaliningondo, Bikina (SPAC/PSPC) (he/him)
	+ bikina.kaliningondo@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca

**Request for Proposal:**

The RCMP is seeking a contractor to provide production-ready components in support of the implementation of a functional system for the CFDSS project. Only suppliers that meet the eligibility requirements are invited to submit their proposals.

**Proposal Submission:**

Please disregard the Ariba Discovery posting response deadline closing time and CanadaBuys posting closing time. All required supporting documentation and bid submission must be submitted by May 30, 2024 at 14
